name: The End of Woman
description:
the woman lost her leg at the end of her journey, she could no longer walk, and she was restrained by something that looked familiar. it is a ring, yes it is a wedding ring ! The ring seems to tell us that if you have found the end of your love journey, then stay there. Do not look for what is not in your partner, but complete it. 

1099 x 1518 px
